🎶The boards are back in town🎶
Custom corn hole boards are once more available for pre-order! The order window starts today (7/26) and runs through August 8th. The set includes two boards and eight regulation bags (4 red and 4 blue). In-store pickup or local delivery only. The sets should arrive the week of 8/29. Don't miss out! To pre-order, head over to the web store (link in bio). 

#cincymade #cornhole #tossemifyougotem

node.text:
It's Franz Friday!
A nod to Cincy’s brewing heritage with a bit of Rhinegeist flair, Franz is our seasonal Oktoberfest bräu. As much at home in a pair of lederhosen as jeans and a t-shirt, Franz is a refreshing climb up the mountain of tradition with a full bodied malt bill and a brisk, clean finish that will pump up your spirits. Franz is a seasonal release, available in the taproom today and in stores starting next week. 

#cincymade #getpumped #maltymountaineer

node.text:
Glow, our vibrant and refreshing Fruited Sour Ale is an illuminating blend of açaí, prickly pear and passionfruit highlighted with a hint of sea salt. When you're doing your thing, Glow is there to throw a little extra shine. Show us how you Glow!

To find Glow near you, head over to the Beer Finder (link in bio). 

#cincymade #glowup #goskate #rollerskating

Franz, our (slightly un-)traditional Oktoberfest Ale featuring a rich and robust malt bill, returns to the taproom this Friday! Wider distro starts next week—keep an eye out for the Malty Mountaineer near you. Local delivery available Fridays (order Mon-Fri by 9am). Dust off those lederhosen and dirndls.

Happy Friday!
We’re proud to be a participant in this year’s @alesforals . Ales for ALS is a national fundraising campaign created in 2013 by a Yakima Valley hop farming family to raise funds and awareness for ALS, or Lou Gehrig’s disease. Each year @loftusranches and @yakimachief donate a unique hop blend, developed by master brewers, to select breweries across the country.

This year’s blend includes Simcoe, Sabro, Mosaic, Citra, Talus, Equanot, and several others. The resulting brew is all about showcasing this diverse, citrus-forward hop bill, and is brimming with orange, pineapple and herbal notes.  $1 from every pint is donated to @alstdi . Our Ales for ALS brew is pouring in the taproom now!

#cincymade #AlesforALS

Mathlete punches way above its weight, delivering a refreshing, full-bodied IPA in 115 calories. Bright, crisp, and unaccountably hoppy, this low-cal IPA works the crowd and scores extra points for style.

Mathlete's back in 6-packs for the season now! To find Mathlete near you, head over to the Beer Finder (link in bio).

The power of perception.
Aged in an oak foeder for 12 months with our house cultures before a healthy addition of passionfruit, Perceptual Passion acquires mild funk, tart acidity and pronounced tropical fruit character. Gold medal winner at the 2018 @fobab in Chicago. Perceptual Passion is a very limited release, available on draft and in 500 mL bottles.
